select *, (SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM events_tracking
LEFT JOIN events ON events.event_id = events_tracking.eventtracking_eventid
WHERE eventtracking_userid = 1
AND events_tracking.eventtracking_status = "unread"
AND events.event_parent_type = "lead"
AND events.eventresource_id = leads.lead_id
AND events.event_item = "comment")
AS count_unread_comments, (SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM events_tracking
LEFT JOIN events ON events.event_id = events_tracking.eventtracking_eventid
WHERE eventtracking_userid = 1
AND events_tracking.eventtracking_status = "unread"
AND events.event_parent_type = "lead"
AND events.event_parent_id = leads.lead_id
AND events.event_item = "attachment")
AS count_unread_attachments, (SELECT first_name
FROM users
WHERE users.id = leads.lead_converted_by_userid)

FROM users

AS converted_by_last_name, (select count(*) from `tags` where `leads`.`lead_id` = `tags`.`tagresource_id` and `tags`.`tagresource_type` = 'lead') as `tags_count`, (select count(*) from `comments` where `leads`.`lead_id` = `comments`.`commentresource_id` and `comments`.`commentresource_type` = 'lead') as `comments_count`, (select count(*) from `attachments` where `leads`.`lead_id` = `attachments`.`attachmentresource_id` and `attachments`.`attachmentresource_type` = 'lead') as `attachments_count`, (select count(*) from `checklists` where `leads`.`lead_id` = `checklists`.`checklistresource_id` and `checklists`.`checklistresource_type` = 'lead') as `checklists_count` from `leads` left join `categories` on `categories`.`category_id` = `leads`.`lead_categoryid` left join `users` on `users`.`id` = `leads`.`lead_creatorid` left join `leads_status` on `leads_status`.`leadstatus_id` = `leads`.`lead_status` where 1 = 1 and `lead_id` = '1' and `lead_visibility` = 'visible' order by `lead_id` desc limit 20 offset 0
